snippet.title: The Legend of Lumina Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer for The Legend of Lumina. Play it here: https://wizbane.itch.io/the-legend-of-lumina

Explore an ancient forest, push blocks to solve puzzles, and search for a way to end the curse on your land.
